
* environ *

Syntax: environ load/save/erase [<digit>]

	Load or save your environment: current sky name, say/tell tones,
	stereo flag, dimension, visibility flag, ignore picture, 
	ignore all users/shouts/tells flags, # of paged lines and wrap and
	hint at help flags. 

	You can save/load different environment files, by using the
	additional <digit> parameter.

	To erase an environment file, use "erase" option.

See also: .run, .arun, .drun
